<summary>XOR textures are cool (11/30/25)</summary>
<p>The xor texture is a really cool texture that takes minimal effort to make, infact, you can even fit it into 128 bytes. Heres a quick demo of what an xor texture looks like:</p>
    <img src="https://lodev.org/cgtutor/images/xortexture.gif">
        <p>Its just a cool default texture, you can read about it in this <a href="https://lodev.org/cgtutor/xortexture.html">cool article</a> i found :)</p>
