        <summary>New super mario brothers. Wii (11/26/2025)</summary>
        <p>New super mario brothers Wii is a video game that has amassed the msot sales over the entire new. series.
            Selling around 12 million copies. Due to the immense popularity, the game obsivly had some kind of key
            sucess factor. I think that the sucess factor of the game was its multiplayer. Multiplayer heavily improveed
            the original game, as the game was finally enjoyable by diffrent types of people.</p>
        <img width="200px" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f3/New_Super_Mario_Bros._Wii_logo.svg">
        <img width="200px" src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/super_mario_wii_2_ars.jpg">
        <p>The immense opoularity of the game was also becuase of the Wii's sucess, and the huge marketing it recieved.
        </p>
        <em>Does it deserve all its fame? And is it a good game in general?</em>
        <p>In my opinion yes, as its fame is derserved. Ignoring marketing campaign's and the Wii's succsess, it is a
            great game. <br>It is in its core, an extremely good game, containing amazing and unique levels, such as the
            jumbo one. The level contains flying jumbo rays flying around, and jumping on one another is extrmeely fun
            and unqiue, among other examples. In conclusion, the game is extrmely fun and I think it is worth a try :)
        </p>
